00:12:09.829 --> 00:12:11.409
so I think it's reasonable to say

00:12:11.409 --> 00:12:14.689
that this is going to be
a substitution reaction.

00:12:14.689 --> 00:12:17.212
Substitution.

00:12:17.212 --> 00:12:19.439
And we substituted with a-

00:12:19.439 --> 00:12:20.991
