00:12:23.197 --> 00:12:25.872
So it involved a neucleophile.

00:12:25.872 --> 00:12:28.253
Nucleophile.

00:12:28.253 --> 00:12:31.496
But this one, unlike the Sn2 reaction,

00:12:31.496 --> 00:12:33.142
in the rate determining step,

00:12:33.142 --> 00:12:34.291
