00:13:08.109 --> 00:13:11.749
and only one reactant is involved

00:13:11.749 --> 00:13:14.236
in the rate determining step.

00:13:14.236 --> 00:13:16.801
So this right over here,
this whole reaction

00:13:16.801 --> 00:13:20.801
